               <code code="34084-4" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="ADVERSE REACTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title>6 ADVERSE REACTIONS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Hypersensitivity reactions with pruritus, edema and rash have been reported in the post-marketing setting.  Have emergency resuscitation equipment and personnel immediately available.
		  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20180706"/>
               <excerpt>
                  <highlight>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Hypersensitivity reactions have occurred; have emergency resuscitation equipment and personnel immediately available <linkHtml href="#s6">(6)</linkHtml>.</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>
                           <content styleCode="bold">To report SUSPECTED ADVERSE REACTIONS, contact 3D Imaging LLC at 501-353-2883 or FDA at 1-800-FDA-1088 or www.fda.gov/medwatch.</content>
                        </paragraph>
                     </text>
                  </highlight>
               </excerpt>
            </section>
